^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Okay, lets talk about the auction, because both Dee and I were optimists. I have 7 hcp plus 1 length point = 8 Sarting Points. Once Dee bids spades  I can add two points for my doubletons for a total of  10 points, just enough for a limit raise. I almsot bid  a constructive raise, since my hand didnt really "feel" like a limit raise, but I decided to play it straight.|
